commit.title: [dumpglob] Remove single glob file mode in favor of one glob per .v
commit.message:
[dumpglob] Remove single glob file mode in favor of one glob per .v

We simplify the dumpglob logic, which now works similarly to aux
files, opening the file will enable dumping.

As a pre-requisite we remove the `File` dump mode, which was used to
produce a single glob file for multiple .v files. Calling coqc on
multiple files is deprecated [problems with state].
